{"tid":2032982,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"on.cc：留香港不留暴民；兩會：移居香港或可保留內地身份","createTime":"2020-05-24T11:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T11:42:14.000Z","uid":288981,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"cde275a5538f355ac88d523d4f266f33e4be381d","tid":2032982,"uid":288981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q90FwiU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq90FwiU.jpg&h=7175b038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dnozALA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdnozALA.jpg&h=de78c5f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國安法劍及履及 留香港不留暴民<br />\n&quot;就當全港有二百萬人支持反對派，這些人若不認同一國，就應該扶老攜幼移民他去，好行夾不送，無謂留在香港搞風搞雨。當這二百萬人離開後，留下來的必須是愛國愛港，尊重一國。中央便可趁此機會，徹底改革行政、立法、司法、教育、房屋等問題，實行留港不留人。香港由亂入治，背靠祖國，便可重新開始。事實上，人口減少，輪候公屋的人龍亦隨之大減，無殼蝸牛可加快上樓；同樣地，人口減少，連帶污染也減少，香港便可實行城市綠化，一舉多得，何樂而不為？明乎此，部分香港人不要以為自己特別矜貴，不要以為香港不能沒有他們，事實是中國有十四億人口，這區區二百萬人算甚麼？<br />\n螞蟻緣槐誇大國，蚍蜉撼樹談何易。隨着中央強硬應對，外部勢力以華制華，利用代理人搞亂香港、遏止中國崛起的把戲到此為止。洋奴漢奸與整個國家作對，注定自取滅亡！&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20200523/mobile/odn-20200523-0523_00186_001.html?from=timeline&amp;isappinstalled=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200523%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20200523-0523_00186_001.html%3Ffrom%3Dtimeline%26isappinstalled%3D0&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=12827321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20200523/mobile/odn-20200523-0523_00186_001.html?from=timeline&amp;isappinstalled=0</a><br />\n<br />\n移居香港或可保留內地身份！兩會重磅提案！<br />\n<br />\n&quot;今年兩會，全國政協委員、中國僑商聯合會常務副會長、香港嘉祥交通(亞洲)集團董事局主席姚志勝提出兩份提案。其中有一項是《允許合法取得香港永久性居民身份證內地人士保留內地身份證》，希望對合法取得香港永久性居民身份證的內地人士，允許其選擇保留內地身份證;對於因過去規定已放棄內地身份證的人士，可以申請補發。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/6q9IpqIBKYMKTgI_L1OFiw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2F6q9IpqIBKYMKTgI_L1OFiw&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=ad438028\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/6q9IpqIBKYMKTgI_L1OFiw</a>"},{"pid":"b0074373422151cf9be1dc26d33ca717030ac9d8","tid":2032982,"uid":248120,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:11:37.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母條死屍啦，留港不留人"},{"pid":"871665cc3a629afa77a3bc4d27badff697162f2f","tid":2032982,"uid":33498,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:12:41.000Z","msg":"見到依d支支<br />\n見一個打一個"},{"pid":"64de3d1e4e4b91cfcbe35c999d13141ffd4f4754","tid":2032982,"uid":298114,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:15:04.000Z","msg":"On9，我係度出世成長讀書做野，我做乜要走，點解我唔可以捍衛自己地方"},{"pid":"a722200469593006e815369b1f4907899e0a6962","tid":2032982,"uid":310700,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:15:42.000Z","msg":"DLLMCH,<br />\nOver my dead body 先啦"},{"pid":"4e8c86a7ebedad8a0bac4e56b5c38f358cf0aa45","tid":2032982,"uid":12911,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:16:40.000Z","msg":"希望剩返係香港既少數派快d離開香港"},{"pid":"e77f071d3df2f1d89e08d281b9cd83b328dd142d","tid":2032982,"uid":54511,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:16:55.000Z","msg":"移居香港 資產收歸祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ac964f1a51280de48d4dafdbdb9cbac488cdb3","tid":2032982,"uid":46500,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:18:02.000Z","msg":"白粉報紙繼續奶啦<br />\n支共真係做低曬反對派之後第一個就係挖你老豆條白粉屍出來鞭打加民心"},{"pid":"1097343cd4769a5132fafa1b6435377483124598","tid":2032982,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:19:19.000Z","msg":"十年前同大陸網民傾偈，佢話香港既優勢係制度同人才"},{"pid":"faec57b46a28b95d082003c45e90fbefb428f7e8","tid":2032982,"uid":169195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:20:31.000Z","msg":"移民唔拘呀, <br />\n鐘意既只係